channel.title: RuneScape Botting
channel.description: Before RSPS I used to make premium scripts, but was bored of runescape so came here.. So I would like to make a script again if you guys have anything you want like a script you never seen before that would be good to use/have PM ME it and i'll consider making it and giving it to just you.

item.title: RuneScape Botting
item.dc:creator: @ghostly150 ghostly150
item.description:
@ghostly150 wrote:

Why do you bot on R|S? It’s dishonorable and it gets annoying for us players stealing resources and/or NPC’s while we are trying to train skills. Also, I’d especially add the spammers as well are very annoying. These days I hate going to the Grand Exchange because you can hardly read a player’s message before it is kicked off screen by a spam bot. Whatever, I’m done with my short rant.
